  "general_provisions": "This bill requires the appropriation of a certain amount of funds in the Public Education Economic Stabilization Restricted Account to a new trust fund for public education.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>establishes the Public Education Economic Stabilization Trust Fund (trust fund) that the state treasurer manages;<hr><ltbullet>provides the duties and authority of the state treasurer regarding the trust fund;<hr><ltbullet>exempts the trust fund from the Money Management Act;<hr><ltbullet>requires the appropriation of a certain amount of funds in the Public Education Economic Stabilization Restricted Account to the trust fund before other statutory one-time appropriations;<hr><ltbullet>corrects the application of a certain minimum appropriation; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
